<section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><h2><strong>Welcome to Hilton Sharp &#038; Clarke</strong></h2>
<h4>Accountancy, Tax and Financial Planning for you, your family and your business</h4>
<p>We can help you reach your Business &#038; Personal Goals through:-</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Proactive advice in plain English</strong></li>
<li><strong>Advice on saving tax and increasing your bottom line</strong></li>
<li><strong>Big firm capability without big firm charges</strong></li>
</ul>
</div></section>
<div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-2  el_after_av_textblock  el_before_av_one_fourth  column-top-margin" ><section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color '  style='color:#969696; '  itemprop="text" ><p><a href="https://www.hsc.uk.net/business-services/accounting/"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-3494" src="https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/business-services-accounting-300x200.jpg" alt="Accounting" width="300" height="200" srcset="https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/business-services-accounting-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/business-services-accounting-705x470.jpg 705w, https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/business-services-accounting-450x300.jpg 450w, https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/business-services-accounting.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.hsc.uk.net/business-services/accounting/">Accounting</a><br />
Whether your business operates as a Limited Company, a Partnership or a Sole Trader you will need accounts prepared.</p>
</div></section></div>
<div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-4  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  column-top-margin" style='border-radius:0px; '><section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><p><a href="https://www.hsc.uk.net/business-services/tax-planning/"><img src="https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/personal-services-personal-tax-planning-300x200.jpg" alt="Tax Planning" width="300" height="200" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-3635" srcset="https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/personal-services-personal-tax-planning-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/personal-services-personal-tax-planning-705x469.jpg 705w, https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/personal-services-personal-tax-planning-450x299.jpg 450w, https://www.hsc.uk.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/personal-services-personal-tax-planning.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.hsc.uk.net/business-services/tax-planning/">Tax Planning</a><br />
